WEBVTT

00:05:59.272 --> 00:06:02.936
I think the world would be
a totally different place outside of work.

00:06:03.624 --> 00:06:08.300
That can happen if business
gets single-minded about racism.

00:06:09.316 --> 00:06:11.789
But the question is:
How is that supposed to happen?

00:06:11.813 --> 00:06:15.594
Well, I think there are three things
that business can borrow from Project '87:

00:06:15.618 --> 00:06:17.084
real problems,

00:06:17.108 --> 00:06:18.301
real numbers,

00:06:18.325 --> 00:06:19.647
real consequences.

00:06:21.235 --> 00:06:22.810
Like it or not,

00:06:23.401 --> 00:06:26.870
diversity is not really a problem
for business -- yet.

00:06:26.894 --> 00:06:30.354
I mean, it's a nice thing to have,
it's the right thing to do,